{
  "info": {
    "name": "School Payments API (Cashfree Sandbox)",
    "_postman_id": "9a7e8b0c-1234-5678-90ab-abcdef123456",
    "description": "Postman collection for testing School Payments backend integrated with Cashfree Sandbox API.\n\n### üîë Sandbox Test Credentials\n\n**Test Card (Visa Debit)**\n- Card Number: 4706131211212123\n- Expiry: 05/2025\n- CVV: 123\n- OTP: 123456\n\n**Netbanking**\n- Bank: HDFC Bank\n- User ID: test\n- Password: test\n\n**UPI**\n- Handle: success@upi\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è Use only these sandbox credentials ‚Äî do not use real cards/UPI.\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Register",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "register"] },
        "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}" }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Login",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
        "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}" }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "let jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "if (jsonData.token) {",
              "  pm.environment.set('token', jsonData.token);",
              "  console.log('‚úÖ Token saved:', jsonData.token);",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('‚ùå Token not found');",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Create Payment (Cashfree)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
        ],
        "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/create-payment", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["create-payment"] },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"order_amount\": 100,\n  \"return_url\": \"https://google.com\",\n  \"student_info\": {\n    \"id\": \"STU1001\",\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"phone\": \"9999999999\"\n  }\n}"
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "let jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "if (jsonData.order && jsonData.order.custom_order_id) {",
              "  pm.environment.set('order_id', jsonData.order.custom_order_id);",
              "  console.log('‚úÖ Order ID saved:', jsonData.order.custom_order_id);",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('‚ùå Order ID not found');",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Check Payment Status (Cashfree)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
        ],
        "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/check-payment-status/{{order_id}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["check-payment-status", "{{order_id}}"] }
      }
    }
  ]
}
